    <segment id="3" parent="16" relname="span">But of course I think at least with this example that Windows error messages are not very useful</segment>
    <segment id="7" parent="14" relname="span"> since the error message doesn&apos;t give us any way to translate the error codes into layman terms ie error x1289xo9a etc .</segment>
    <segment id="4" parent="10" relname="span">This would require some translation</segment>
    <segment id="9" parent="4" relname="unless"> unless you were a windows qualified expert .</segment>
    <segment id="5" parent="6" relname="nonvolitional-cause">The average user is not going to understand these error codes.</segment>
